{"tid":940603,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"34C港姐歐陽巧瑩馬爾代夫全裸曬太陽","createTime":"2018-12-14T05:26:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-17T17:45:36.000Z","uid":79563,"like":43,"dislike":133,"uniUserReply":101,"replies":[{"pid":"f90d236221e173fcc8d5191edde803dc5dcf4916","tid":940603,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:26:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181214/large/1544760554_d8c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181214%2Flarge%2F1544760554_d8c9.jpg&h=8c4355df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺節目《3日2夜》經常以三點式泳衣出鏡，憑34C成網民熱話嘅前港姐歐陽巧瑩（Tammy）。上月23號跟「木偶哥」林師傑結婚，但因為工作關係，佢哋今個月至可以出發去馬爾代夫度蜜月。<br />\n<br />\n林師傑同Tammy一向都好鍾意陽光與海灘，一去到當地就急不及待大解放。今日凌晨木偶哥兩公婆齊齊喺Instagram晒股，貼咗一張兩人全裸嘅相。照片清楚見到佢哋喺酒店屋前泳池一絲不掛，露出白滑嘅屁股，趴喺池邊望住無邊大海，睇嚟非常寫意。照片隱約見到Tammy手持一部航拍遙控器，相信照片係出自佢手筆。Tammy話﹕「拍拖四周年快樂，多謝老公完成咗我十八歲嘅心願，辛苦咗成個2018，終於好好放鬆五日。」原來今次係上集度蜜月，因為Tammy話﹕「返香港搏殺半個月，一月再出發蜜月Part Two(容許我哋放肆一下 ，呢度實在太正喇)。」<br />\n<br />\n木偶哥就用咗鍾舒祺《裸泳》嘅歌詞，話經過今次「坦誠相對」之後，兩個人嘅路至會行得更遠。識睇睇留言，唔少網友都表態支持，仲紛紛提出疑問，有網友問「好奇究竟邊個影」、「肉色泳衣？兩位都好白滑喎」、「估唔到佢囉由（屁股）咁圓喎」、「兩個去三個邊？」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181214/large/1544761239_3f3d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181214%2Flarge%2F1544761239_3f3d.jpg&h=4ced39a1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"04a01361b9049e9f0e60c4d32ff74c002c1226eb","tid":940603,"uid":38904,"like":648,"dislike":5,"score":643,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:31:42.000Z","msg":"肯定喺個泳池度中出幾百發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4059de4a907d8e7ff3cf347dbc35a1e7f019e896","tid":940603,"uid":96196,"like":150,"dislike":4,"score":146,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:32:03.000Z","msg":"無碼相呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e77f74569d9c4d73fa5203434ec6c0dba1b4417","tid":940603,"uid":67500,"like":588,"dislike":11,"score":577,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:33:59.000Z","msg":"2條友都惡形惡相，難怪觀眾緣差"},{"pid":"fe1a72f24db1116f73a8d1a8a798a5de37c6efab","tid":940603,"uid":19712,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:34:45.000Z","msg":"咁遠都打格"},{"pid":"b2d9b8e543e1c52b9ccd155756cfd386fa7b2880","tid":940603,"uid":38757,"like":100,"dislike":5,"score":95,"quote":{"pid":"6e77f74569d9c4d73fa5203434ec6c0dba1b4417","tid":940603,"uid":67500,"like":588,"dislike":11,"score":577,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:33:59.000Z","msg":"2條友都惡形惡相，難怪觀眾緣差"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:35:16.000Z","msg":"邊個黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我google 完好似完全無見過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aab3c25ca825613c3dc9ccd0f9c35cfda880905b","tid":940603,"uid":13936,"like":5,"dislike":55,"score":-50,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:36:06.000Z","msg":"個記者一定影左正面收埋內部J"},{"pid":"e6d2586a45a1dc475ed5e019dd882bd21e7823ba","tid":940603,"uid":103156,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:36:49.000Z","msg":"衰埋一堆"},{"pid":"c5efdafeed03a6b900071bccaf4e14d2b04eedfe","tid":940603,"uid":1377,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"4059de4a907d8e7ff3cf347dbc35a1e7f019e896","tid":940603,"uid":96196,"like":150,"dislike":4,"score":146,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:32:03.000Z","msg":"無碼相呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T05:36:53.000Z","msg":"ig咪有囉"},{"pid":"d676400ad7a7881e9292c20d6268528495